@node Introduction
@chapter Introduction
@cindex introduction
@cindex overview

@cindex MCP
@cindex Model Context Protocol
OwnSona is a single-user, self-hosted memory server.  It stores durable
facts about you in a PostgreSQL database and exposes them over the
@uref{https://modelcontextprotocol.io, Model Context Protocol (MCP)} so
that any MCP-capable large-language-model client --- Claude (Anthropic),
ChatGPT (OpenAI), Gemini (Google), Grok (xAI), and an ever-growing list
of others --- can read from and write to the same store.

The name is a contraction of @emph{own persona}.  The store is your
persona, the part of yourself you teach once and never have to teach
again.

